				<div style="clear: left;">
															<p>These additional articles may be of additional assistance:</p>
<p>Family Basics by SchwabLearning<br />
<a href="http://www.iffcmh.org/A%20Parents%20Guide%20to%20Family%20Basics.pdf" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://www.iffcmh.org/A%20Parents%20Guide%20to%20Family%20Basics.pdf</a></p>
<p>Learning Disabilities and Sibling Issues:<br />
<a href="http://www.ldonline.org/article/Learning_Disabilities_and_Sibling_Issues" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://www.ldonline.org/article/Learning_Disabilities_and_Sibling_Issues</a></p>
<p>It can be challenging at times t find the correct balance.  Best wishes.<br />
</p>
